data.description: Welcome to your new home! This spacious and well-built condo offers a fantastic opportunity to reside in a low-maintenance community with water views. The open floor plan of the main living area boasts an updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an island. The living room was also recently updated with LVP flooring. All three bedrooms are generously sized with two bedrooms featuring their own en-suite bathroom. Upstairs, there is private loft with an additional bedroom and bathroom that adds versatility to the living space. Step outside onto the open deck from the living area, creating the perfect setting for entertaining friends and family. Enjoy a range of amenities, including a pool, kayak launch, marina, clubhouse, exercise room, and paved trails along the waterfront. With dedicated off-street parking on an interior corner lot, convenience is at your doorstep.  Don't miss this chance to make this delightful condo your home sweet home!
